{"tid":1818760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平林鄭月娥頭像貼天橋  防暴警徒手清理","createTime":"2020-01-10T07:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T02:16:39.000Z","uid":52001,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"84e006ecc4112cb09ccf540d2e3f8a5d0bf9fce0","tid":1818760,"uid":52001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3127353427372692&amp;id=715486135226112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3127353427372692%26id%3D715486135226112&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=061fea60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3127353427372692&amp;id=715486135226112</a><br />\n<br />\n有網民發起「中環和你Lunch」活動，下午約一時在環球大廈對開行人天橋聚集，參加者戴上口罩、有人舉標語並叫口號，有人天橋貼上國家主席習近平、行政長官林鄭月娥、警務處處長鄧炳強及多名官員的頭像紙張。一批防暴警察其後到場，分別徒手及用鉗、鏟、萬用刀等工具清理各人紙張。<br />\n<br />\nSource:RTHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bcLuUvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcLuUvm.jpg&h=a6420f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e107d9a87e413429d8ae1e133d8733c7ce3a128","tid":1818760,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:25:07.000Z","msg":"偶像崇拜都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0f59d036a5478b503c88a29d2b501dd60f01be","tid":1818760,"uid":321674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bed20caa286edf70297f89e2ae62fe11725aff2","tid":1818760,"uid":52001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid